Description: Desktop interface for SigmaVault NAS OS
SigmaVault Desktop is a modern GTK4 application for managing your
SigmaVault NAS system. It provides comprehensive monitoring and control
over compression jobs, storage management, agent swarm coordination,
and system configuration.
.
Features:

- Real-time dashboard with system metrics
- Compression job management with detailed progress tracking
- Storage management: disks, ZFS pools, datasets, and network shares
- Elite Agent Collective monitoring (40-agent swarm)
- System settings: network configuration, service management
- Beautiful libadwaita interface with dark mode support
  .
  Built with Python, GTK4, and libadwaita for a modern, responsive
  user experience.
